<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821692>
    dc:description "FIGURES 546–550. Lymaenon spp. 546, L. pygmaeus (Girault), head, anterior; 547, L. pygmaeus (Girault), head, posterior, 548a, L. ornatus (Gahan), head, lateral; 548b, male lateral (internal) showing ocular apodeme; 549, L. sp., head, anterodorsal; 550, L. pygmaeus (Girault), antenna. antenna. Scale bars=100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821692/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821694>
    dc:description "FIGURES 551, 552. Lymaenon spp., mesosoma. 551, L. pygmaeus (Girault), female, dorsal; 552, L. ornatus (Gahan), male, lateral. Scale bars=100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821694/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821696>
    dc:description "FIGURES 553, 554. Lymaenon pygmaeus (Girault). 553, mesosoma, ventral; 554, wings. Scale bars=100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821696/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

